Catalano.Imaging.Filters

Class LevelsCurve

  • java.lang.Object
    • Catalano.Imaging.Filters.LevelsCurve
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBaseInPlace

    public class LevelsCurve
extends java.lang.Object
implements IBaseInPlace
    Curve correction of RGB channels.

    The filter performs curve correction of RGB channels by mapping specified channels' input ranges to output ranges.
